Version 0.2.5 - 2010-04-13 (RDS)
------------------------------

	+ src/WishInterpreter.cc         - If no grouping options have been chosen then
					   each spectral bin is assigned to its own group.

Version 0.2.4 - 2010-04-12 (RDS)
