	+ config/specgroup.par           - Included overwrite=yes option

Version 0.2.2 - 2010-03-11 (RDS)
------------------------------

	+ src/Specgroup.cc/h,
	  src/WishInterpreter.cc/h       - Made more compatible with RGS.
