					   from the SPECQUAL CCF.
						(SPR-6596)
					   
Version 0.2.1 - 2010-03-04 (RDS)
------------------------------

	+ src/Specgroup.cc/h,
	  src/WishInterpreter.cc/h       - Made compatible with RGS
